QuestData.Title: Assault on the Temple of Sha'naar
QuestData.Description:
Up in the hills of Tanaan Jungle, the Sargerei have converted a once-sacred temple into a den of demonic summoning.
We must attack them now, before their rituals complete. The longer we delay, the stronger our enemy grows.
QuestData.LogDescription: Assault the Sargerei forces at the Temple of Sha'naar in Tanaan Jungle.

Objectives.Objective: Assault the Sargerei forces at the Temple of Sha'naar
